hopobject.body: Will I get paid for overtime? albuterol sulfate and ipratropium bromide side effects Prime Minister Manmohan Singh's administration has pledgedto tackle chronic power shortages that hobble the growth ofAsia's third-largest economy. But power companies are saddledwith debt. Power stations do not have enough coal or gas to runat full capacity, and state-run distribution companies are toobroke to pay for the power that utilities produce.
